Class RestockData

java.lang.Object
plasystem_functions.RestockData
public class RestockData extends Object
Represents a single restocking event in the PlaSystem database, mapping to the Restock table. Each event includes a unique ID, date and time details, and a list of associated restock items. Provides getters and setters for accessing and modifying the event's attributes.
